    {
      "id": "el_14",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 403,
      "width": 414,
      "height": 234,
      "text": "sqrt(a x b) = sqrt(a) x sqrt(b)\nsqrt(a / b) = sqrt(a) / sqrt(b)\nRationalize: 1/(sqrt(a)+sqrt(b)) =\n(sqrt(a)-sqrt(b))/(a-b)\nNested: sqrt(sqrt(x)) = x^(1/4) = 4th root\n  cube_root(sqrt(x)) = x^(1/6) = 6th root\n\nWHY: (sqrt(a)×sqrt(b))^2 = a×b, so\nsqrt(a×b)=sqrt(a)×sqrt(b)\n  Rationalize uses (x+y)(x-y)=x^2-y^2 to clear surds\n\nEx: sqrt(50)=sqrt(25×2)=5sqrt(2)\n1/(sqrt(5)+sqrt(3))=(sqrt(5)-sqrt(3))/(5-3)=(sqrt(5)-\nsqrt(3))/2\n✓",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 1400,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 14,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f3"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "sqrt(a x b) = sqrt(a) x sqrt(b)\nsqrt(a / b) = sqrt(a) / sqrt(b)\nRationalize: 1/(sqrt(a)+sqrt(b)) =\n(sqrt(a)-sqrt(b))/(a-b)\nNested: sqrt(sqrt(x)) = x^(1/4) = 4th root\n  cube_root(sqrt(x)) = x^(1/6) = 6th root\n\nWHY: (sqrt(a)×sqrt(b))^2 = a×b, so\nsqrt(a×b)=sqrt(a)×sqrt(b)\n  Rationalize uses (x+y)(x-y)=x^2-y^2 to clear surds\n\nEx: sqrt(50)=sqrt(25×2)=5sqrt(2)\n1/(sqrt(5)+sqrt(3))=(sqrt(5)-sqrt(3))/(5-3)=(sqrt(5)-\nsqrt(3))/2\n✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
