    {
      "id": "el_41",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1162,
      "width": 310,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Make exponents equal\n  2^30 = (2^3)^10 = 8^10\n  3^20 = (3^2)^10 = 9^10\nStep 2: 9>8 → 9^10 > 8^10\n\nTRICK:\nLCM of exponents, then compare bases\nOr use logs: 30×0.301=9.03 vs 20×0.477=9.54\n3^20 wins!\n\n  2^30 = 8^10 ─┐\n                ├─ 8 < 9 → 3^20 wins\n  3^20 = 9^10 ─┘\n\nAnswer: 3^20 is larger ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 4100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 41,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
