    {
      "id": "el_56",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1543,
      "width": 296,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Multiply by conjugate\n  5(√3-√2) / (√3+√2)(√3-√2)\nStep 2: = 5(√3-√2) / (3-2) = 5(√3-√2)\n\nTRICK:\n(√a+√b)(√a-√b) = a-b\nMultiply top & bottom by conjugate\nDenominator becomes rational integer\n\n     5         5(√3-√2)     5(√3-√2)\n  ─────── × conjugate = ─────── = ───────\n  √3+√2                  3-2        1\n\nAnswer: 5(√3-√2) ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 5600,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 56,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_7"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Multiply by conjugate\n  5(√3-√2) / (√3+√2)(√3-√2)\nStep 2: = 5(√3-√2) / (3-2) = 5(√3-√2)\n\nTRICK:\n(√a+√b)(√a-√b) = a-b\nMultiply top & bottom by conjugate\nDenominator becomes rational integer\n\n     5         5(√3-√2)     5(√3-√2)\n  ─────── × conjugate = ─────── = ───────\n  √3+√2                  3-2        1\n\nAnswer: 5(√3-√2) ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
