      "width": 224,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Simplify each surd\n  √50=5√2, √18=3√2, √72=6√2\nStep 2: 3(5√2)+2(3√2)-6√2\n  = 15√2+6√2-6√2 = 15√2\n\nTRICK:\nSimplify all to same surd first\nThen add/subtract like terms\nOnly LIKE surds can combine!\n\n  3×5√2 + 2×3√2 - 6√2\n  = (15 + 6 - 6)√2 = 15√2\n\nAnswer: 15√2 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
