    {
      "id": "el_76",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1909,
      "width": 245,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Nearest square: 64=8²\n  d = 68-64 = 4\nStep 2: √68 ≈ 8 + 4/(2×8) = 8.25\n  Actual: 8.246\n\nTRICK:\n√N ≈ p + (N-p²)/(2p)\nwhere p² is nearest perfect square\nWorks great for quick estimation!\n\n  64 ── 68 ── 81\n  8²         9²\n  √68 ≈ 8 + (68-64)/(2×8) = 8.25\n\nAnswer: √68 ≈ 8.25 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 7600,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 76,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_11"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Nearest square: 64=8²\n  d = 68-64 = 4\nStep 2: √68 ≈ 8 + 4/(2×8) = 8.25\n  Actual: 8.246\n\nTRICK:\n√N ≈ p + (N-p²)/(2p)\nwhere p² is nearest perfect square\nWorks great for quick estimation!\n\n  64 ── 68 ── 81\n  8²         9²\n  √68 ≈ 8 + (68-64)/(2×8) = 8.25\n\nAnswer: √68 ≈ 8.25 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
