        "type_12"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 7056 = 2⁴×3²×7²\n  All even powers → perfect square\n  √7056 = 84\nStep 2: 2744 = 2³×7³ = 14³\n  All powers ÷3 → perfect cube\n\nTRICK:\nSquare: all prime powers even\nCube: all prime powers divisible by 3\nUnit digit check first (quick filter)\n\n  7056 = 2⁴ × 3² × 7²  (all even → ✓ square)\n  2744 = 2³ × 7³        (all ÷3  → ✓ cube)\n\nAnswer: √7056=84, ∛2744=14 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
