    {
      "id": "el_91",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 2290,
      "width": 281,
      "height": 260,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: √(√256) = 256^(1/4)\n  256=4⁴ → 4th root = 4\nStep 2: ∛(√729) = 729^(1/6)\n  729=3⁶ → 6th root = 3\n\nTRICK:\nNested roots → MULTIPLY exponents\n√ then √ = 4th root (1/2×1/2=1/4)\n√ then ∛ = 6th root (1/2×1/3=1/6)\n\n  √(√256) = (256)^(1/2×1/2) = 256^(1/4)\n  256 = 4⁴ → (4⁴)^(1/4) = 4\n\n  ∛(√729) = (729)^(1/2×1/3) = 729^(1/6)\n  729 = 3⁶ → (3⁶)^(1/6) = 3\n\nAnswer: 4 and 3 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 9100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 91,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_14"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: √(√256) = 256^(1/4)\n  256=4⁴ → 4th root = 4\nStep 2: ∛(√729) = 729^(1/6)\n  729=3⁶ → 6th root = 3\n\nTRICK:\nNested roots → MULTIPLY exponents\n√ then √ = 4th root (1/2×1/2=1/4)\n√ then ∛ = 6th root (1/2×1/3=1/6)\n\n  √(√256) = (256)^(1/2×1/2) = 256^(1/4)\n  256 = 4⁴ → (4⁴)^(1/4) = 4\n\n  ∛(√729) = (729)^(1/2×1/3) = 729^(1/6)\n  729 = 3⁶ → (3⁶)^(1/6) = 3\n\nAnswer: 4 and 3 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
