    {
      "id": "el_96",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 2290,
      "width": 267,
      "height": 274,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: LCM(2,3,4)=12, raise all\n  2^(1/2)=(2⁶)^(1/12)=64^(1/12)\n  3^(1/3)=(3⁴)^(1/12)=81^(1/12)\n  4^(1/4)=(4³)^(1/12)=64^(1/12)\nStep 2: 64=64<81\n\nTRICK:\nLCM the exponent denominators\nRaise to make same root\nThen compare the bases inside\n\n  All → 12th root:\n  2^(1/2) → 64^(1/12)\n  3^(1/3) → 81^(1/12)  ← largest\n  4^(1/4) → 64^(1/12)\n  64 = 64 < 81\n\nAnswer: 2^(1/2) = 4^(1/4) < 3^(1/3) ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 9600,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 96,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_15"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: LCM(2,3,4)=12, raise all\n  2^(1/2)=(2⁶)^(1/12)=64^(1/12)\n  3^(1/3)=(3⁴)^(1/12)=81^(1/12)\n  4^(1/4)=(4³)^(1/12)=64^(1/12)\nStep 2: 64=64<81\n\nTRICK:\nLCM the exponent denominators\nRaise to make same root\nThen compare the bases inside\n\n  All → 12th root:\n  2^(1/2) → 64^(1/12)\n  3^(1/3) → 81^(1/12)  ← largest\n  4^(1/4) → 64^(1/12)\n  64 = 64 < 81\n\nAnswer: 2^(1/2) = 4^(1/4) < 3^(1/3) ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
